What is age.90 population structure of origin?

ggplot(data=usdataset)+geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Origin, y=Age.90,colour=Age.90))

From this graph we could find there is around one third of population at age 90 is not Hispanic, while population at age 90 has about 1300000 are not Hispanic.
